OL,3,CMore than 2,000 prosecuted in
OL,4,Cshoplifting crackdown
OL,6,FMore than 2,000 shoplifters have been
OL,7,Fprosecuted in a crackdown on rising
OL,8,Fcrime, Lancashire Police say.
OL,10,FIt comes after figures revealed the
OL,11,Fabuse some shop workers are forced to
OL,12,Fsuffer as a result of shoplifting.
OL,14,FA survey by the retail union USDAW
OL,15,Ffound that in the past 12 months, 69%
OL,16,Fof workers have experienced verbal
OL,17,Fabuse, while 17% were assaulted while
OL,18,Fat work with 70% of these incidents
OL,19,Fwere triggered by shoplifting.
