OL,3,CMore than 2,000 prosecuted in
OL,4,Cshoplifting crackdown
OL,6,FOverall, there has been a 29% increase
OL,7,Fin thefts from retailers in England
OL,8,Fand Wales in the past year.
OL,10,FMark Malone, USDAW, said: "It's almost
OL,11,Fan age of lawlessness. There is no
OL,12,Fconsequence to shoplifting, it's very
OL,13,Fvery minimal.
OL,15,F"Our members face violent abuse and
OL,16,Fthreatening behaviour at work on a day-
OL,17,Fday-to-day basis."
