OL,3,CMore than 2,000 prosecuted in
OL,4,Cshoplifting crackdown
OL,6,FStaff who work for the shopping
OL,7,Fretailer Boots in Preston say they
OL,8,Fhave noticed the difference a police
OL,9,Fpresence has made to shoplifting and
OL,10,Foverall safety.
OL,12,FAbbie Paxton, Customer Adviser at
OL,13,FBoots, said: "So much safer in the
OL,14,Fstore. We know that we can ring them
OL,15,Fnow and they will come in minutes.
OL,17,F"We got to the point where we
OL,18,Fliterally gave up reporting at one
OL,19,Fpoint because it was just backlogged
OL,20,Fand we did not have the police coming
OL,21,Fin every day."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
