OL,3,CMore than 2,000 prosecuted in
OL,4,Cshoplifting crackdown
OL,6,FStaff at the Boots in Preston city
OL,7,Fcentre also wear bodycam, but believe
OL,8,Fthe police operation is working.
OL,10,FOperation Vulture has seen officers
OL,11,Fpatrolling shops and streets since
OL,12,FMarch 2024.
OL,14,FBoots staff member Lisa Barber said:
OL,15,F"It just gives us reassurance that we
OL,16,Fhave got some protection on the shop
OL,17,Ffloor incase somebody does get abusive
OL,18,For even violent."
