OL,3,CMore than 2,000 prosecuted in
OL,4,Cshoplifting crackdown
OL,6,FAntipoverty campaigners say that the
OL,7,Fcost of living crisis is forcing
OL,8,Fpeople into stealing food, baby
OL,9,Fformula and even nappies.
OL,11,FLancashire Police insist those people
OL,12,Fwill be helped to seek help, but crime
OL,13,Fcannot pay.
OL,15,FClive Grunshaw, Lancashire Police and
OL,16,FCrime Commissioner, said: "Whatever
OL,17,Freason people may give, that's no
OL,18,Fexcuse for committing criminal
OL,19,Fbehaviour."
